NK071(du)007:1: // sgyu 'phrul lam rim gyi bsdus don 'phrul gyi lde mig zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK071(du)007:3: ma dpe ldeb dang po chad rjes su rnyed na gso rogs zhu /
NK071(du)007:4: nas spyir bstan pa la gnyis rigs la 'gyur ba med pas dpe rgyal po lta bu /
NK071(du)007:5: lam dang 'bras bu gzhan med pa'i dpe lha 'phrul dga' lta bu'o //
NK071(du)007:7: dbye ba bye brag tu bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:8: de ltar don bsdus te bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:15: dbyer med kyi gnas tshul lo //
NK071(du)007:17: lam rang la gnas tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:18: rdo rje phung po 'bras bu rang la gnas tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:19: kun rdzob chu zla la mtshon pa'i dpe don no //
NK071(du)007:21: gsang rgyud rang la gnas tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:22: rgyud don rang la gnas tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:23: de dag lam lang pa ma yin pa'i 'thad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:25: 'bras bu bstan pa rang la gnas pa dang /
NK071(du)007:26: rgyu gleng gzhi rang la gnas tshul lo //
NK071(du)007:29: dal bzhi tshig gi bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:30: gleng gzhi rang la gnas tshul la gsum /
NK071(du)007:33: de dag gleng gzhir gyur pa'i 'thad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:34: rgyud don gnas tshul la brgyad /
NK071(du)007:37: ba snyen sgrub dang thig la /
NK071(du)007:42: spyod pa rang rig la gnas tshul lo //
NK071(du)007:47: dar gyi tsakra la tshang ba dang /
NK071(du)007:48: spyir 'khor lo bzhi la tshang ba'o //
NK071(du)007:49: don dam gnas tshul la drug /
NK071(du)007:50: chos kun don du gcig pa dang /
NK071(du)007:51: nges tshig dang dpe thun mong ba dang /
NK071(du)007:52: de nyid chos nyid kyi skur bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:53: de las lam dang 'bras bu gzhan na med pa dang /
NK071(du)007:54: rang byung ye shes chos kun gyi dngos gzhir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:56: dbyer med gnas tshul la gsum /
NK071(du)007:57: 'khor 'das dben pa dbyer med du gcig pa'i dpe don dang /
NK071(du)007:58: gdod nas dbyer med du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:59: gnyis su snang yang gnyis su ma grub pa'o //
NK071(du)007:60: gnyis pa lam la mtshan nyid gsum las /
NK071(du)007:61: dang po rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid rang gnas mthong ba'i le'u la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:62: rtsom pa dang 'brel ba'i don dang /
NK071(du)007:67: de la don bcu bzhi las /
NK071(du)007:68: dang po dgos pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:69: ma rtogs par bsgom pa'i skyon dang /
NK071(du)007:70: des na rtogs pa'i thabs la 'bad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:75: sbyangs pas snod du gyur pa dang /
NK071(du)007:76: rin gyis snod du gyur pa'o //
NK071(du)007:77: dang pol la gnyis rgyu mtshan gyi tshul gyis mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:83: sbyangs pa rgyun du 'gro bar lung gi 'thad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:88: skye bar byed pa'i rgyu rkyen dang /
NK071(du)007:90: skye bar byed pa'i rgyu rkyen la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:107: gnas pa gsum gyi dang po thos bsam mo //
NK071(du)007:108: rin gyis snod du gyur pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:112: ma sbyangs par 'jug pa'i 'thad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:120: rgyu rkyen dang ldan pas 'jug pa'o //
NK071(du)007:122: thun mong gi thog par 'jug pa dang /
NK071(du)007:126: rgyu rkyen du ldan pas sems skye tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:127: snod kyi yon tan dang ldan pas thos pa don du gnyer ba'o //
NK071(du)007:128: gsum pa dus la gnyis su sbyar /
NK071(du)007:129: rgyu rkyen gnyis thun mong du bshad na gsum /
NK071(du)007:130: shes par byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK071(du)007:131: lhan gcig byed pa'i rkyen dang /
NK071(du)007:133: drug pa rtogs thabs la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:137: de dus rten la dbabs pa dang /
NK071(du)007:138: nor ba'i shes rab mig gi gsal ba dang /
NK071(du)007:139: ma nor dmigs nas blangs pa'o //
NK071(du)007:147: dang po rten tshig 'byung ba'i gzhi dang /
NK071(du)007:148: yongs su brtan pa'i gzhi gnyis su yang 'dod na /
NK071(du)007:149: 'dir ni yongs su brtags pa'i gzhi la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:150: gzhal bya gang la brtag pa dang /
NK071(du)007:151: de la dogs pa spang ba'o //
NK071(du)007:152: de la gnyis dpyad kyis mi lang ba'i dogs pa spang ba dang /
NK071(du)007:153: gzhal du mi btub pa'i dgos pa spang ba'o //
NK071(du)007:158: yul du shes pa la gzhal du mi btub pa'o //
NK071(du)007:170: ngo bo nyid kyi gsung gi tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:173: mngon par byang chub pa'i dang /
NK071(du)007:175: sprul sku'i gsung gi tshul lo //
NK071(du)007:180: shes rab kyi rjes su mtshon par gdams pa dang /
NK071(du)007:181: dngos dang tshul gyi rjes su mtshon par gdams pa'o //
NK071(du)007:183: tshig lnga so sor bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:184: mdor gnyis su bsdus te bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:189: ngo bo'i gsung mtshon pa'i tshig dang /
NK071(du)007:195: gsang ba'i gsung mtshon pa'i tshig go //
NK071(du)007:196: mdor gnyis su bsdus te bstan pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:200: dpyad du na sas go ba dang /
NK071(du)007:203: dpyad du na sas 'thad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:204: dpyad du na sa'i don dang /
NK071(du)007:206: ma dpyad par rtogs pa'i dpe don dang rtogs pa'i don dang /
NK071(du)007:208: dpyad pas go ba la gsum /
NK071(du)007:210: dam tshig dang ldan par bya ba dang /
NK071(du)007:211: don dang tshig gcig dang tha dad kyi dgos pa bsal te don du go bar gdams pa'o //
NK071(du)007:217: tshig don mi mthun pa dang /
NK071(du)007:218: tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK071(du)007:221: gtan tshig dbab bya'i don dang /
NK071(du)007:224: gtan la dbab tu btub pa'i 'thad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:228: de la bstan du na sa dang /
NK071(du)007:231: ci yang yin min gyi gtan tshig dang /
NK071(du)007:232: mtha' dang bral ma bral gyi gtan tshigs so //
NK071(du)007:233: tshigs don mthun pa'i gtan tshig la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:240: dag mnyam thun mong pa dang /
NK071(du)007:244: rgyas pa gnyis kyis rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs so //
NK071(du)007:245: sgra mthun don dpag la bzhi /
NK071(du)007:249: mtshon pa dpe'i gtan tshigs so //
NK071(du)007:251: dpe yi sa don rtogs pa'i 'thad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:253: nor ba'i shes rab dmigs gis bsal ba thun mong la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:258: nor ba'i shes rab dmigs kyis bsal ba'o //
NK071(du)007:263: gol ba dngos la gnyis 'jig rten par gol ba dang /
NK071(du)007:271: lam rgyud lnga gol ba spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:272: khams gsum gyi lha mir gol bar byed brag tu bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:277: rgyu'i theg par gol ba dang /
NK071(du)007:282: bla na med pa'i theg par gol ba'o //
NK071(du)007:285: de las sngags khyad par du spags pa'o //
NK071(du)007:288: bden pa gnyis kyi ngo bo yis dang /
NK071(du)007:289: gnyis su med pa yis dang /
NK071(du)007:291: snang ba mi spang pas 'phags pa'o //
NK071(du)007:293: bla na med pa'i theg pa'i gzhung dang /
NK071(du)007:294: thabs kyi theg pa de las spang tshul lo //
NK071(du)007:295: sngags phyi par gol ba la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:298: ma nor dmigs nas blang ba la bzhi /
NK071(du)007:299: ma nor ba'i don gyi ngo bo dang /
NK071(du)007:301: tshig tu mtshon pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK071(du)007:302: de su'i yul yin pa'i sgo nas gdam pa'o //
NK071(du)007:307: lta ba tha dad ci snang yang de kho na nyid las ma g.yos pa dang /
NK071(du)007:308: mnyam pa'i don ngos gzungs bral bar bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:309: byang chub kyi mtshan nyid do //
NK071(du)007:312: de nyid dmigs su med par bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:313: de nyid chos kun gyi ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:315: yod med du tshol ba'i skyon dang /
NK071(du)007:316: btsal du med pa'i dpe don no //
NK071(du)007:320: gnyis ka las tshol ba'i skyon no //
NK071(du)007:321: tshig tu mtshon pa'i dgos pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:322: ming gis rnam grangs du mar bstan pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK071(du)007:323: don smra brjod dang bral bar bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:324: rang gi ngo bo dang rnam grangs thun mong du bstan pa la gsum /
NK071(du)007:338: yul med rang gsal du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:339: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis na du bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:340: rnam grangs la gnyis ming gi rnam grangs dang /
NK071(du)007:343: mthong ba spyan gyi lta ba dang /
NK071(du)007:349: nyon yid bdag na sa'i dang /
NK071(du)007:350: kun gzhi thams cad mkhyen pa'i lta ba'o //
NK071(du)007:351: don gyi rnam grangs dngos la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:352: lam rim gyi lta ba dang /
NK071(du)007:358: zag bcas kyi lam bye brag tu bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:359: lam dgu mkhyen spyir bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:362: de rgyu gang las byung ba dang /
NK071(du)007:376: sngags dang phyag rgya'i lta ba'o //
NK071(du)007:377: dgu pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:385: de la khyad par yod pa'i dpe don dang /
NK071(du)007:390: shes rab chen po'i sbyin sreg dang /
NK071(du)007:391: lam la gzhan don rdzogs pa'i che ba'o //
NK071(du)007:392: bcu pa phan yon la bzhi /
NK071(du)007:393: 'khor bar mi ldog pa'i phan yon dang /
NK071(du)007:399: bcu gsum pa rtogs pa'i tshad la dpe gnyis /
NK071(du)007:400: rang gi mtshan nyid mthong ba dang /
NK071(du)007:401: gsal cha khyad par du gyur pa'o //
NK071(du)007:402: tha ma ma rtogs pa'i skyon la gsum /
NK071(du)007:404: don la bskur bar gdam pa dang /
NK071(du)007:405: bsgom pa dang 'brel ba'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)007:407: ngan song du ltung ba dang /
NK071(du)007:409: don la bskul bar gdam pa la bzhi /
NK071(du)007:410: don tshig ldan par gdam pa dang /
NK071(du)007:411: ma rtogs pa'i nyes pas don mi 'grub pa dang /
NK071(du)007:413: gsal bar gyis gcig par gdams pa'o //
NK071(du)007:414: spyi don gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:415: rtsom pa dang 'brel ba'i don dang /
NK071(du)007:447: dgag sgrub med pa'i bcos thabs dang /
NK071(du)007:448: gzung 'dzin med pa'i bcos thabs so //
NK071(du)007:451: bsrung du na sa'i dam tshig go //
NK071(du)007:455: gzhan nas thob tu med pa'o //
NK071(du)007:457: dpe'i sgo nas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:461: bsgom bya lta ba'i dpe don no //
NK071(du)007:463: dang po stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:469: rgyas pa la bco lnga las /
NK071(du)007:470: dang po sngon du 'gro ba la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:471: thun mong spyi dang khyad par 'di nyid kyi sngon 'agro'o //
NK071(du)007:473: dbang thob cing lhag pa'i yo byad lnga dang ldan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:475: gnas khang gdan dang ldan par bya ba dang /
NK071(du)007:476: bsod nams kyi dpung bskyed pa dang /
NK071(du)007:477: phyi nang gi 'brel gcad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:478: cha rkyen bsdu zhing bar chad bsrung ba'o //
NK071(du)007:479: gnyis pa dgos pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:480: go rim nyes par gzhag pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK071(du)007:481: ngo bo smos pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK071(du)007:485: ngo bo smos pa'i dgos pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:492: chos nyid don du gnyer ba dang /
NK071(du)007:493: ting nge spyi'i dgos pa dang /
NK071(du)007:494: dngos grub don du gnyer ba dang /
NK071(du)007:495: ting nge na sa'i skyon no //
NK071(du)007:496: gsum pa sgom pa'i thabs la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:505: gdam ngag gi stobs kyis gzhag pa dang /
NK071(du)007:506: shes rab kyi stobs kyis gzhag pa'o //
NK071(du)007:508: gzhag thabs ma nor ba dang /
NK071(du)007:514: cig car spyi blugs su bzhag pa dang /
NK071(du)007:515: lta ba mthong ba'i rjes su gzhag pa'o //
NK071(du)007:517: chos kun de bzhin nyid du bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:518: chos dang chos can gnyis na du bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:519: bsam pa'i yul med par bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:520: cir yang mi bsam par bsgom pa'o //
NK071(du)007:521: lta ba mthong ba'i rjes su gzhag pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:522: chos nyid kyi don gang gis rtogs pa dang /
NK071(du)007:523: rtogs pa'i don gyi ngo bo'o //
NK071(du)007:531: gzhag thabs nor pa la gsum /
NK071(du)007:533: 'jug tu na pa'i che ba dang /
NK071(du)007:534: dmigs na nor ba'i dpe don no //
NK071(du)007:535: bzhi pa ngo bo la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:546: rnam grangs bzhir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:549: rgyu'i theg pa chen po'i dang /
NK071(du)007:552: rnal 'byor chen po'i de bzhin nyid do //
NK071(du)007:555: de re re'ang ngo bo nges tshig gtan tshig dang gsum ldan du bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:557: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel ba dang /
NK071(du)007:558: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med dang /
NK071(du)007:559: don de sgom pa'i rim pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)007:562: don la ma zhen pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)007:564: bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK071(du)007:569: bar du gcod pa'i skyon bcu dang /
NK071(du)007:570: sgrib par rtsa ba yan lag gi skyon dang bzhi rtogs pa las gyur pa'i skyon dang /
NK071(du)007:571: khams las gyur pa'i rkyen dang /
NK071(du)007:572: spyod lam las gyur pa'i skyon no //
NK071(du)007:573: drug pa bcos thabs la gsum /
NK071(du)007:574: blo dang sbyar te bcos thabs gsum gyis bcos pa dang /
NK071(du)007:575: dgag sgrub na sa'i bcos thabs dang gnyis kyis rtog pa'i skyon bcos pa dang /
NK071(du)007:576: khams kyi skyon bcos pa dang /
NK071(du)007:577: spyod lam gyi skyon bcos pa'o //
NK071(du)007:588: brgyad pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:592: bdag don dang gzhan don no //
NK071(du)007:594: shes rab dang mthun pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)007:595: spyod lam thams cad tshogs gnyis su spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)007:597: gzhan don gyi spyod pa la gsum /
NK071(du)007:598: bdag don la gzhan don rdzogs pa'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:599: rgyud gzhung gi spyod pa kun lta sgom 'brel ba spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)007:600: gzhan don du 'gyur la lam gong ma bsgoms te don bya ba'o //
NK071(du)007:601: dgu pa dam tshig la gsum /
NK071(du)007:602: khyad par kyi dam tshig dang /
NK071(du)007:603: spyi'i dam tshig ji ltar ldan pa'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:604: lam gong 'og gi dam tshig la khyad par yod pa'i dpe don no //
NK071(du)007:612: de dam tshig tu gzhag pa'i 'thad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:614: drod gsum spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:615: phyi yul la snang ba dang /
NK071(du)007:616: nang sems la snang ba gnyis kyis drod kyi dbye ba dang /
NK071(du)007:618: bcu gcig pa rtags la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:619: drod rtags bstan pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK071(du)007:642: zag med kyi mngon shes so //
NK071(du)007:646: zag med kyi mngon shes la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:648: rgyu'i byang chub sems dpa'i mngon shes dang gnyis kyi khyad par ro //
NK071(du)007:653: bcu gnyis pa rmi lam la bzhi /
NK071(du)007:654: sgrib pa dag cing don mthong ba'i rmi lam dang /
NK071(du)007:655: lhas byin gyis rlob pa'i rmi lam dang /
NK071(du)007:658: de bla ma min pa la gsang ba'o //
NK071(du)007:662: bcu gsum pa phan yon la bdun /
NK071(du)007:663: rgyu las dge sdig gis ma gos pa dang /
NK071(du)007:664: 'bras bu rnam smin bde sdug gis ma gos pa dang /
NK071(du)007:665: spyod pa rtsang sme na sa dang /
NK071(du)007:666: 'khor ba ma spang bral ba dang /
NK071(du)007:669: mtshan ma zil gyis gnon pa'i phan yon no //
NK071(du)007:670: bzhi pa 'das ka ma la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:673: bco lnga pa 'bras bu chos sku thob par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:674: gnyis pa snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor la gnyis las /
NK071(du)007:676: lus snga ma dang mthun par bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:677: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:680: gnyis pa dgos chad la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:682: ting la 'jug pa'i thun mtshams nyams dang sbyar ba'o //
NK071(du)007:686: gsum pa sgom pa'i thabs la gsum /
NK071(du)007:688: de'i tshe ba tshad med bzhi rdzogs pa'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:689: des na rgyu'i theg pa'i snying rje las khyad par du gyur pa'o //
NK071(du)007:694: so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyi rgyu yis sgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:695: lam lnga ma goms pa'i rjes la bsgom pa'o //
NK071(du)007:697: chos kun rang rgyud pas stong pa'i dpe dang /
NK071(du)007:698: rang gzhan gcig dang tha dad las grol ba'i 'thad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:700: lam snga ma gom pa'i rjes la bsgom pa la /
NK071(du)007:702: cig car spyi blugs su bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:703: yul dang bral ba bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:704: bsgom thabs yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)007:705: rnam pa ngo bo la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:709: ngo bo dang grangs thun mong pa dang /
NK071(du)007:712: bsgom bya'i don gyi ngo bo dang /
NK071(du)007:713: sgom byed ting nge'i ngo bo'o //
NK071(du)007:714: dang po la sgyu ma'i dngos po drug /
NK071(du)007:732: thun mong gi skyon phra la nyung ba dang /
NK071(du)007:733: khyad par gyi skyon cha dbye ba'o //
NK071(du)007:734: drug pa bcos pa'i thabs la gsum /
NK071(du)007:742: gnyen po bsten pa la gsum /
NK071(du)007:748: zhen par dag pas nyams lngar snang ba mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:749: nyams lngar rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:750: de la lnga g.yo ba dang /
NK071(du)007:755: brgyad pa spyod pa la gsum /
NK071(du)007:756: sngon 'byung rgyal ba'i mdzad pa dper bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:757: rjes 'jug rnal 'byor pa'i spyod pa don du bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:759: snang la ma zhen par rtog pa'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:765: sgyu ma ltar spyod pa'i yon tan dang /
NK071(du)007:766: snying rje chen po'i spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)007:767: tshad na bzhi'i spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)007:768: bsgom pa la gzhan don tshang ba dang /
NK071(du)007:769: rgyu'i theg pa'i snying rje las spags pa'o //
NK071(du)007:776: ye shes rang gsal gyi spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)007:777: gnyis su na sa'i spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)007:778: dngos po nyi shu la ye shes su spyad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:779: dgu pa dam tshig la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:783: khyad par gyi dam tshig dang /
NK071(du)007:784: thun mong gi dam tshig go //
NK071(du)007:785: bcu pa drod la dbye ba na /
NK071(du)007:786: bcu gcig pa rtags la bzhi /
NK071(du)007:793: bcu gsum pa phan yon la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:794: phan yon tshad med pa dang /
NK071(du)007:795: tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing phyag rgya cig pa la sbyor ba'o //
NK071(du)007:796: bcu bzhi pa 'das ka ma la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:799: bco lnga pa 'bras bu la gsum /
NK071(du)007:801: mthar thug longs sku thob pa dang /
NK071(du)007:802: ma rtogs par le lo byas pa'i skyon no //
NK071(du)007:803: gsum pa phyag brgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:805: lus snga ma dang rjes mthun du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:806: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:808: dang po sngon du 'gro ba dang /
NK071(du)007:809: gnyis pa dgos pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:815: gsum pa bsgom pa'i thabs la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:818: de la gnyis sems sbyangs pa dang /
NK071(du)007:824: a la sems sbyang ba dang /
NK071(du)007:828: phrin las kyi rim pa dang /
NK071(du)007:838: spyir gang mos su bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:839: khyad par du rdo rje sems dpar bsgom pa'o //
NK071(du)007:841: phra mo rim gyis pa dang /
NK071(du)007:844: rgyu yi yi ge bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:845: de yi khyad par las gdan dang gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:851: rtsa ba'i lha bskyed pa dang /
NK071(du)007:852: yan lag gi lha bsgom pa'o //
NK071(du)007:854: cho ga gsum gyis sku phra mo bskyed pa dang /
NK071(du)007:855: de goms nas sku yongs su rdzogs par bsgom pa'o //
NK071(du)007:860: de goms nas sku yongs su rdzogs par bsgom pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:861: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa dang /
NK071(du)007:863: yan lag gi lha la gsum /
NK071(du)007:868: blo che ba cig car bsgom pa dngos dang /
NK071(du)007:869: gzhal yas khang la sogs pa snga ma dang mthun par bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:872: bsgom thabs gnyis mthun par bstan pa dang //
NK071(du)007:873: zhi ba las bsgyur te bsgom pa'o //
NK071(du)007:876: rigs bzhi la bsgyur te bsgom pa'o //
NK071(du)007:877: bzhi pa ngo bo la gsum /
NK071(du)007:878: ngo bo rig pa rang snang du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:879: ngo bo lhun grub tu bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:885: drug pa bcos thabs la gsum /
NK071(du)007:888: spyod lam gyi skyon bcos thabs so //
NK071(du)007:892: rtsol ba drag zhan nyams dang sbyar ba'o //
NK071(du)007:893: brgyad pa spyod pa la gsum /
NK071(du)007:896: ting nge brtan pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)007:898: spyod lam gyi bye brag zhi khro'i skabs dang sbyar ba dang /
NK071(du)007:899: bdag nyid chen po'i mchod pa'i yon tan dang /
NK071(du)007:900: dus thams cad du ting nge 'dzin dang ma bral ba'i yon tan dang /
NK071(du)007:901: bya ba spangs pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)007:902: spyod pa dag cing brtson pa'i yon tan dang /
NK071(du)007:906: bcu gcig pa rtags dag ma bzhi grub pa dang po'i rtags dang /
NK071(du)007:911: snga ma dang khyad par dang /
NK071(du)007:913: bcu gnyis pa rmi lam gsum /
NK071(du)007:914: legs nyes gsal brten du 'byung ba dang /
NK071(du)007:915: grub pa'i rmi ltas bcu bzhi dang /
NK071(du)007:916: zad sar gyi skye mched bcu gsum mthong ba'o //
NK071(du)007:917: bcu gsum pa sgom pa'i phan yon la gsum /
NK071(du)007:918: dngos dang zhar la skyon bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:919: mthong mos kyi yon tan no //
NK071(du)007:931: nan tan chung ba'i skyon dang /
NK071(du)007:934: bco lnga pa 'bras bu la gsum /
NK071(du)007:937: tshe 'di la ma thob dang skye ba rgyud pa gzhan la thob par gdam pa'o //
NK071(du)007:938: spyi don bzhi pa phyag rgya spros pa'i skabs kyi don la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:942: dang po sngon du 'gro ba la gsum /
NK071(du)007:943: ting nge 'dzin snga ma brtan pas brtan khang du bshams pa dang /
NK071(du)007:944: mchod pa dgram zhing cha rkyen bsdu ba dang /
NK071(du)007:945: sngon du 'gro ba'i las rim dngos so //
NK071(du)007:947: bdag gi dang gzhan don gyi dgos pa'o //
NK071(du)007:948: gsum pa bsgom thabs la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:976: rigs lnga re mos su bslabs pa dang /
NK071(du)007:980: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa la bslab pa'o //
NK071(du)007:984: khro bo la bslab pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:991: zhal phyag spros la bslab pa'o //
NK071(du)007:994: gnyis brgya dgu bcu'am stong gnyis brgya lnga bcu la bslab pa'o //
NK071(du)007:998: goms nas phrin las byang chub la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1001: bzhi pa ngo bo la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1006: mtshan ma lnga la zhen pa'i dang /
NK071(du)007:1007: bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad dang /
NK071(du)007:1009: bdud kyi spyod yul la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1011: shes ma shes khyad par ro //
NK071(du)007:1012: drug pa bcom thabs dang bzhi ste /
NK071(du)007:1013: snga ma'i rjes su sbyar ro //
NK071(du)007:1024: brgyad pa spyod pa la gsum /
NK071(du)007:1025: lta spyod kyi dpe don dang /
NK071(du)007:1029: tshogs gnyis su spyad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1030: lta spyod 'brel ba spyad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1034: 'dod yon gyi lha mor spyad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1035: thog pa na sar spyad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1036: blo dang sbyar te spyad pa'i thabs so //
NK071(du)007:1037: spyod pa'i ting nge la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1043: dgu pa dam tshig la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1047: ting nge 'dzin gyi dam tshig dang /
NK071(du)007:1048: bsrung du na sa'i dam tshig dang /
NK071(du)007:1049: gzhan don du kun bsrung ba'o //
NK071(du)007:1053: sngon bas stobs che ba 'byung ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1056: rtags la re dogs spang pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1057: bcu gnyis pa rmi lam la gsum /
NK071(du)007:1058: rmi ltas kyi khyad par dang /
NK071(du)007:1059: bzang po'i ltas kun 'byung ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1060: de'i 'thad pa'i tshul gyis bar chad med pa dang ltas mthun pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1061: bcu gsum pa phan yon la gsum /
NK071(du)007:1062: rtogs tshogs lha'i dal du rang snang ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1063: lha rig pa rang snang du sgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1064: bsgom pas zhen pa dag pas 'bras bu 'byung ba'o //
NK071(du)007:1065: bcu bzhi pa 'da' ka ma la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1066: 'da' ka ma bsgom pa'i phan yon dang /
NK071(du)007:1067: nus pa zhan pas ma bsgom kyang rgyud nas 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1071: spyi don lnga pa bar chad med par tshogs bsgrub pa la gnyis las /
NK071(du)007:1074: de nyams su blangs pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK071(du)007:1083: thabs kyi bsnyen bsgrub 'og tu kha 'phang ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1084: bsgrub pa'i bsnyen bsgrub gtso bor bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1095: phun sum tshogs pa lngas gzhi gzung ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1096: bsnyen bsgrub kyis gzhung bsrang ba'o //
NK071(du)007:1105: sgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1115: khang bu brtsegs te byug cing brgyan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1121: dag pa bsdus te byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1122: lnga pa sgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1123: gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub kyis gzhung bsrang ba gnyis gong du bshad na gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1124: bsnyen sgrub kyis gzhung bsrang ba dngos dang /
NK071(du)007:1125: de'i grogs yo byad la spyad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1144: ting nge 'dzin gyi dal bskyed pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1145: ye shes kyi dal spyan drangs shing sdud pa'i las rim mo //
NK071(du)007:1153: tshom bu spyir sgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1159: de'i grogs yo byad la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1163: yo byad la spyad pa'i mdor bstan dang sbyor sgrol khro bor kha 'phang ba thun mong ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1164: yo byad lnga la spyad pa rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1166: mtshan ma med pa'i spyad thabs zhi khro thun mong ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1167: mtshan ma dang bcas pa'i spyad thabs so //
NK071(du)007:1173: des grub pa'i don gyis mtshan ma med pa'i spyad thabs dngos so //
NK071(du)007:1174: mtshan ma dang bcas pa'i spyad thabs la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1178: snod bcud gzhal yas khang dang lhar bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1179: ting nge 'dzin gcig pus spyad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1182: gzhal yas khang lhar dang bcas pa'i don dang /
NK071(du)007:1183: yan lag la lha rig lngar bsgom pa'i yon tan dang /
NK071(du)007:1184: yan lag bskyod pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)007:1185: so so'i spyad thabs la bzhi /
NK071(du)007:1186: gos rgyas la spyad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1187: bro gar glu tshig gi spyad thabs thun mong ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1188: bzang btung la spyad thabs dang /
NK071(du)007:1189: a li ka li la spyad thabs so //
NK071(du)007:1191: gos la spyad pa'i yon tan dang /
NK071(du)007:1192: rgyan la spyad pa'i thabs dang /
NK071(du)007:1193: spyi don 'dod yon lnga la spyad pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)007:1194: bro gar glu tshig thun mong du spyad thabs la lnga /
NK071(du)007:1195: de gnyis thun mong gi yon tan dang /
NK071(du)007:1196: gtso bo'i bro bya ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1197: dbang po lnga la yi ge bkod de 'phro 'du byas pa'i yon tan dang /
NK071(du)007:1198: yab yum spyi'i ting nge dang /
NK071(du)007:1199: rigs so so'i bro glu byas pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)007:1200: bza' btung la spyad thabs la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1201: bza' btung la spyad pas mchod sbyin gnyis su 'gyur ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1202: thun mong gi dngos grub 'grub bo //
NK071(du)007:1203: a li ka li la spyad pa lnga /
NK071(du)007:1205: bsnyen bsgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1207: 'bras bu lha'i dal du 'chal ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1208: thun mong gi dngos grub pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1211: ye shes bla ma'i sa thob pa gnyis kyis mchog gi 'bras bu spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1212: thun mong gi 'bras bu so sor bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1215: yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)007:1221: a li ma la spyad pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)007:1222: gnyis pa khro bo tshogs sgrub pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1229: gnas phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1235: ting nge'i mthu mnyam pas bsgrub pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1241: dang po la gnyis 'tsho ba dang bsgrub pa'i yo byad thun mong pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1242: rkyen bzlog gi yo byad gsum bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1245: re dogs na sar bsgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1247: spyi'i bsnyen bsgrub sngar dang mthun pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1251: grogs yo byad la spyad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1262: yo byad byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1263: phyi mchod bya zhing cha gsum btang ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1264: bsrung ba'i 'khor los mtshams phur gdab pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1272: ting nge'i dal bskyed pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1273: rim gyi dal spyan drangs shing mchod pa'i las rim dang /
NK071(du)007:1280: ji ltar bsgom pa'i thabs so //
NK071(du)007:1289: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ri gas kyis gtso bo byas pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1290: de rigs gzhan la yang sbyar ba'o //
NK071(du)007:1291: spyan drangs shing sdud pa'i las rim la gsum /
NK071(du)007:1293: rig pa'i me tog dor ba'i sngags dang /
NK071(du)007:1294: mchod pa dbul ba'i sngags so //
NK071(du)007:1304: bzlas pa'i ting nge 'dzin spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1305: rtags byung na dngos grub blang thabs so //
NK071(du)007:1309: dngos grub blang thabs dngos dang /
NK071(du)007:1311: gnyis pa grogs byed pa'i yo byad la spyad thabs la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1312: zhi bar khas blangs pa'i gsang ba'i mchod pa rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1313: yo byad thun mong pa bzhi la spyad thabs so //
NK071(du)007:1315: bshad pa dam bca' ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1317: ma rtogs par spyad pa'i nyes pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1323: des mi gos pa'i 'thad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1325: sbyor sgrol tha dad med pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1327: mngon du phyung ba'i sgrol ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1333: stong gsum yongs su sgrol gyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK071(du)007:1334: thabs chen po'i sgrol ba la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1337: des mi gos pa'i 'thad pa la bzhi /
NK071(du)007:1338: bden pa gnyis kyi gtan tshig dang /
NK071(du)007:1340: rnam par shes pa bsgral du na sa dang /
NK071(du)007:1341: sems kyi rang bzhin la bsgral du med par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1343: mngon du phyung ba'i sbyor ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1344: rang bzhin dang dbang po yul dus kyi sbyor ba thun mong pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1351: sgrol sbyor don la tha dad med par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1358: ting nge 'dzin gyi che ba dang bcas pas tshogs su 'gyur ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1359: rdzas bsten pa'i phan yon no //
NK071(du)007:1363: yo byad la spyad thabs la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1364: spyad thabs dang spyad pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK071(du)007:1366: mtshan ma na sa'i spyad thabs zhi ba dang thun pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1367: mtshan bcas kyi spyad thabs so //
NK071(du)007:1369: rtogs pa dang ldan na spyod yul lhar gsal ba dang /
NK071(du)007:1370: yan lag la lha bsgoms pa'i yon tan dang //
NK071(du)007:1371: gom pa dor ba'i yon tan dang //
NK071(du)007:1372: bro gar gyi tshe yan lag lnga bskyod pa'i yon tan dang /
NK071(du)007:1373: yan lag bskyod de sprul pa spros pa'i yon tan dang /
NK071(du)007:1374: yo byad la spyad thabs zhi ba las bsgyur te spyad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1376: spyi don gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub kyi 'bras bu la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1384: skye ba phyi ma la thob pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1385: lan grangs gzhan la thob pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1387: tshe dbang thob pa dngos dang /
NK071(du)007:1388: des sangs rgyas thob tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:1389: des na rag las pa'i sems dor te bcom par 'bad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1390: skye ba phyi ma la thob pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1400: sangs rgyas mi bzhugs pa'i zhing dang /
NK071(du)007:1403: tsha ba'i dmyal ba brgyad du mi skye ba'o //
NK071(du)007:1411: phrin las phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1412: rnam smin thob pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1414: skye ba phyi ma'am lan grangs gzhan la thob pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1421: skye ba phyi ma'am lan grangs gzhan la thob pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1424: spyi don gyi tha ma 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i
NK071(du)007:1425: mtshan nyid kyi skabs kyi don la ga sum ste
NK071(du)007:1426: mthong lam dang / bsgom lam dang /
NK071(du)007:1435: rgyu dus thun mong pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1438: dgongs spyod kyi ming gang las grags pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1445: rnam smin gyi nges tshig go //
NK071(du)007:1449: dgongs spyod kyi ming gang las grags pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1451: lhag na kyi 'das par 'bras bu cha nas brjod pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1453: rtogs pa gnas 'gyur gyi dpe don dang /
NK071(du)007:1454: tha snyad dang bral bar bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1456: rdo rje lta bus mtshan ma bcom pa'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:1457: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis bag chags sbyangs pa'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:1458: don rtogs nas ting nge 'dzin gnyis thob pa bdud bcom pa'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)007:1460: bye brag tu bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1462: spyi don tha mar mthar thug gi 'bras bu la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1463: rtsom pa dang 'brel ba'i don dang /
NK071(du)007:1475: ma 'bras rnam grangs su snang ba'i ngo bo'o //
NK071(du)007:1477: mtshan gyi rnam grangs kyi khyad par mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1478: ngo bo lhun grub gyis grub pa'i dpe dang /
NK071(du)007:1479: mtshan nyid mtha' dang bral ba'i 'thad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1480: mtshan gyi rnam grangs kyi don rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1481: ma 'dres rnam grangs su snang ba'i ngo bo la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1489: ston pa sku lnga dngos dang /
NK071(du)007:1493: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku dang /
NK071(du)007:1498: 'khor gyis go tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1500: rim pa byin gyis brlabs kyi dang /
NK071(du)007:1505: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK071(du)007:1509: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK071(du)007:1510: yang na thugs lnga ste kyus gsal /
NK071(du)007:1516: las bzhis don byed tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:1517: lhun gyis grub pa las las bzhir snang ba'o //
NK071(du)007:1520: bye brag tu bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1526: gzhan gyi rtogs pa dgag pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1527: rang gi 'thad pa brjod pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1528: de la brtsad pa spang ba'o //
NK071(du)007:1529: tha dad pa 'dod pa'i rtog pa dgag pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1530: brtsad pa spang ba la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1531: gcig dang tha dad drang don du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1532: nges don du 'dod pa la gnod pa brjod pas de nyid bsgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1534: rigs pa'i skyon dang lung gi skyon no //
NK071(du)007:1542: ming grangs kyi khyad par ro //
NK071(du)007:1545: bde bar gshegs pa dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i khyad par dang /
NK071(du)007:1546: rgyal ba dang bcom ldan 'das kyi khyad par dang /
NK071(du)007:1547: dgos pa chen po dang longs spyod chen po'i khyad par ro //
NK071(du)007:1549: theg pa thun mong gi gshegs tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:1550: theg pa 'di nyid kyi gshegs tshul khyad par 'phags pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1552: mdo sde'i theg mong pa dang /
NK071(du)007:1558: de gnyis kyi grol lam gyi gshegs tshul dang /
NK071(du)007:1559: thabs lam dbang gi gshegs tshul lo //
NK071(du)007:1562: bya ba rgyud kyi gshegs tshul lo //
NK071(du)007:1564: bde bar gshegs tshul dang de bzhin gshegs /
NK071(du)007:1565: rgyal ba dang bcom ldan 'das kyi khyad par la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1569: theg pa gzhan gyis gzhung dang /
NK071(du)007:1571: sangs rgyas kyi sa'i khyad par la gnyis /
NK071(du)007:1573: theg pa thun mong gi sa gsum drang don du bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1575: dang mi 'phrad par dmod gzugs pa'o //
NK071(du)007:1576: sgyu 'phyul lam rim gyi bsdus don /
NK071(du)007:1577: 'phrul gyis lde mig zhes bya ba /
